cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper involves image processing, data processing, and artificial intelligence techniques to classify plants based on their leaves. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses a neural network for classification, which suggests it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves feature extraction and classification, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of a probabilistic neural network suggests it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
